PureCircle Incurs $3.7 Million Full-Year Net Loss on Lower Sales

-- B y   A l a n   P u r k i s s
-- 
2011-09-19T06:06:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/purecircle-incurs-3-7-million-full-year-net-loss-on-lower-sales.html
PureCircle Ltd. (PURE) , which makes
sweeteners, said it incurred a full-year net loss of $3.7
million in the fiscal year to June 30, compared with a $1.2
million profit in the year-earlier period. Sales fell 12 percent
to $53.3 million.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alan Purkiss at 
 apurkiss@bloomberg.net  